features: PREMIUM QUALITY: Take your home decor to the next level with our 8x12 inches wall decor sign made from high quality lightweight aluminum.

WEATHERPROOF: Our metal wall decor sign is especially treated against UV, humidity and water thanks to our ink curation. As a result, it will not rust or fade which makes it perfect to use indoor and outdoor.

EASY INSTALLATION: Our metal wall art sign comes with 2 pre-drilled holes for an easy installation. It can be mounted with screws, nails or zip ties (NOT INCLUDED) on any walls or fences. We left you the easy part... You just have to make sure it is straight!
GLOSS FINISH: We apply a gloss finish on all our decorative signs to make sure colors are vivid and bright so it can be seen and noticed by your guests from across the room.

UNIQUE DESIGNS AND GRAPHICS: We put a lot of thought and time the design process of our art set. We are proud to offer you the best selection of novelty signs, as well as the best variety of funny and informative designs
description: Home Decor Wall Sign Vertical Rectangle/Wall Art Picture Frame

Make any room of your house look better with our decor signs as it fits many atmospheres and can be farmhouse wall decor, country decor, rustic bathroom decor, family wall decor and even wedding decor. We bring all your good memories such as family vacations, portraits, pets, weddings, birthdays and anniversaries to life.

Our designs are professionally printed with state-of-the-art equipment guaranteed to last for years. We have more than 12 years of experience in the printing industry to offer you stunning detail and rich lifelike colors. All prints are carefully made in our lab in Tampa, Florida.
ADD CHARM & ELEGANCE TO YOUR HOME!

** High quality aluminum ** Perfect for indoor & outdoor ** Treated against UV and water to last for years ** Back wood mounting panels for an easy and straight installation ** Gloss finish for a nice visual effect and vivid colors ** Design professionally printed

GREAT GIFTS IDEA: Unforgettable and unique, it is the perfect birthday gifts, anniversaries, graduations, housewarming, bachelor parties, Christmas, Father’s Day, housewarming, Mother’s Day or any other celebrations.
